---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pageLayout: inner
showLoader: false
showRail: false
---
<section class="chapter chapter--light contact-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb contact-hero__crumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="{{ '/' | url }}">
        <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.breadcrumbHome }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.breadcrumbHome }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.breadcrumbHome }}</span>
      </a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
      <span>
        <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.contact }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.contact }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.contact }}</span>
      </span>
    </nav>
    <header class="chapter__head">
      <span class="chapter__num reveal">12</span>
      <p class="eyebrow reveal">
        <span class="lang en">{{ i18n.en.contact }}</span>
        <span class="lang vi">{{ i18n.vi.contact }}</span>
        <span class="lang zh">{{ i18n.zh.contact }}</span>
      </p>
      <h1 class="chapter__title">
        <span class="lang en">
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line">Let’s Grow the Future</span></span>
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line line--muted">Together.</span></span>
        </span>
        <span class="lang vi">
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line">Cùng kiến tạo</span></span>
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line line--muted">tương lai bền vững.</span></span>
        </span>
        <span class="lang zh">
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line">携手共创</span></span>
          <span class="line-mask"><span class="line line--muted">可持续未来。</span></span>
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="chapter__desc reveal" data-delay="200">
        <span class="lang en">Whether you're looking for a trusted manufacturing partner, logistics solutions or long-term strategic collaboration — tell us how we can help.</span>
        <span class="lang vi">Đối tác sản xuất, giải pháp logistics hay hợp tác chiến lược — hãy cho chúng tôi biết bạn cần hỗ trợ gì.</span>
        <span class="lang zh">无论您需要可靠的制造伙伴、物流方案还是长期战略合作——告诉我们如何为您服务。</span>
      </p>
    </header>
  </div>
</section>
{{ content | safe }}
